Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我允许你加入「演出自我的少女会」  秋筱姬香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  姬儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多关照啊  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  既然社员变成四个人了  我有新的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\1c6B4A56\bord0\shad0}演出自我的少女会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs18\1c6B4A56\bord0\shad0}关于暑假集训！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集训？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假也要进行社团活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为趁暑假偷懒不做社团活动  还能登顶万人迷甲子园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:22:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲子园？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像万人迷这样不要脸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我冬海爱衣来终结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\1c9C8A90\bord0\shad0}决定废社！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  决定废社哦
